<body style="margin:0;padding:0">
<div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide responsive" data-ride="carousel">
  <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block responsive">
    <h1>Desh Travel Blogs</h1>
    <p>Me and VB (my husband) love to travel different places, specially we like to explore wild life. Before every trip we try to read about the place, do and don't etc but struggle to get complete information at single place. Which inspired me to create this site to share my experience with others to help them in better planning for their trips. </p>
  </div>
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <div class="carousel-item active">
      <img class="d-block w-100" alt="First slide" <%= image_tag('img1.jpg')%>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block w-100"  alt="Second slide" <%= image_tag('img2.jpg')%>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block w-100"  alt="Third slide" <%= image_tag('img3.jpg')%>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
  </a>
  <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="next">
    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
  </a>
</div>
</body>
